        </profile>
      </profiles>
      <rules>
        <rule id="99bd-27d1-bedd-b2f2" name="Digi-lasers" hidden="false">
          <description>Hannibus has a set of highly advanced lasers built into the fists of his power armour. These are used before any blows in close-combat are struck and will wound a single foe on a 4+ with normal saves allowed. In addition they count as an extra close-combat weapon and thus give him +1 attack for weilding two weapons.</description>
        </rule>
      </rules>
